{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"WebAssembly.Module","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly/Module","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects\">JavaScript 标准库</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly\"><code>WebAssembly</code></a></strong></li><li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>方法</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly/compile\"><code>WebAssembly.compile()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly/compileStreaming\"><code>WebAssembly.compileStreaming()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly/instantiate\"><code>WebAssembly.instantiate()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly/instantiateStreaming\"><code>WebAssembly.instantiateStreaming()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly/validate\"><code>WebAssembly.validate()</code></a></li></ol></li><li><strong>Related pages:</strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly/Module\"><code>WebAssembly.Module</code></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly/Global\"><code>WebAssembly.Global</code></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly/Instance\"><code>WebAssembly.Instance</code></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly/Memory\"><code>WebAssembly.Memory</code></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly/Table\"><code>WebAssembly.Table</code></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly/CompileError\"><code>WebAssembly.CompileError</code></a></strong></li><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly/LinkError\"><code>WebAssembly.LinkError</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly/RuntimeError\"><code>WebAssembly.RuntimeError</code></a></strong></li><li><strong>继承</strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object\"><code>Object</code></a></strong></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>属性</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/constructor\"><code>Object.prototype.constructor</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/proto\"><code>Object.prototype.__proto__</code></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>方法</strong></a><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineGetter__()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineSetter__()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupGetter__()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\"><strong><code>WebAssembly.Module</code></strong>&nbsp;对象包含已经由浏览器编译的无状态 WebAssembly 代码，可以高效地<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Worker/postMessage\">与 Workers 共享</a>、<a href=\"/en-US/docs/WebAssembly/Caching_modules\">缓存在 IndexedDB 中</a>，和多次实例化。</div>\n\n<div id=\"sect3\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div id=\"sect4\"><code>WebAssembly.Module()</code> 构造函数可以用来同步编译给定的 WebAssembly 二进制代码。不过，获取&nbsp;<code>Module</code>&nbsp;对象的主要方法是通过异步编译函数，如&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly/compile\"><code>WebAssembly.compile()</code></a>，或者是<a href=\"/en-US/docs/WebAssembly/Caching_modules\">通过 IndexedDB 读取 Module 对象</a>.</div>\n\n<div id=\"sect5\">&nbsp;</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"构造函数语法","title":"构造函数语法","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"warning notecard\" id=\"sect6\">\n<p><strong>警告：</strong>由于大型模块的编译可能很消耗资源，开发人员只有在绝对需要同步编译时，才使用&nbsp;<code>Module()</code> 构造函数；其他情况下，应该使用异步 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly/compile\"><code>WebAssembly.compile()</code></a> 方法。</p>\n</div>\n\n<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var myModule = new WebAssembly.Module(bufferSource);</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参数","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"buffersource\"><em>bufferSource</em></dt>\n <dd>一个&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Typed_arrays\">类型化数组</a>&nbsp;或&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer\">ArrayBuffer</a>，包含要编译的 .wasm 模块的二进制代码。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"module_构造函数的方法属性","title":"<code>Module</code> 构造函数的方法属性","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"webassembly.module.customsections_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly/Module/customSections\"><code>WebAssembly.Module.customSections()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>给定&nbsp;<code>Module</code>&nbsp;对象和字符串，通过该字符串，返回&nbsp;Module 对象中所有自定义部分的内容的副本。</dd>\n <dt id=\"webassembly.module.exports_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly/Module/exports\"><code>WebAssembly.Module.exports()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>给定&nbsp;<code>Module</code>&nbsp;对象，返回一个数组，内容是所有已声明的接口的描述。</dd>\n <dt id=\"webassembly.module.imports_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly/Module/imports\"><code>WebAssembly.Module.imports()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>给定&nbsp;<code>Module</code>&nbsp;对象，返回一个数组，内容是所有已声明的引用的描述。</dd>\n</dl>","titleAsText":"Module 构造函数的方法属性"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"module_实例","title":"<code>Module</code>&nbsp;实例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>所有&nbsp;<code>Module</code>&nbsp;实例继承自&nbsp;<code>Module()</code> 构造函数的<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly/Module\">原型对象</a>&nbsp;—— 修改它会影响所有&nbsp;<code>Module</code> 实例。</p>","titleAsText":"Module 实例"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"实例属性","title":"实例属性","isH3":true,"content":"<p>{{page('/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly/Module/prototype', 'Properties')}}</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"实例方法","title":"实例方法","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Module 实例没有自己的默认方法。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">规范</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状态</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">注释</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://webassembly.github.io/spec/js-api/#webassemblymodule-objects\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">WebAssembly JavaScript Interface<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">WebAssembly.Module()</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Working Draft</span></td>\n   <td>定义初稿</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"javascript.builtins.WebAssembly.Module","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly/Module/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect7\">\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"另请查阅","title":"另请查阅","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/WebAssembly\">WebAssembly</a> 概览页面</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/WebAssembly/Concepts\">WebAssembly 概念</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/WebAssembly/Using_the_JavaScript_API\">使用 WebAssembly JavaScript API</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"构造函数语法","id":"构造函数语法"},{"text":"<code>Module</code> 构造函数的方法属性","id":"module_构造函数的方法属性"},{"text":"<code>Module</code>&nbsp;实例","id":"module_实例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"另请查阅","id":"另请查阅"}],"summary":"所有 Module 实例继承自 Module() 构造函数的原型对象 —— 修改它会影响所有 Module 实例。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"WebAssembly.Module","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"WebAssembly.Module()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"WebAssembly.Module","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"WebAssembly.Module","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/webassembly/module","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/webassembly/module/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript","title":"JavaScript"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference","title":"JavaScript 参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects","title":"JavaScript 标准内置对象"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly","title":"WebAssembly"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/WebAssembly/Module","title":"WebAssembly.Module"}],"pageTitle":"WebAssembly.Module - JavaScript | MDN","noIndexing":false}}